to compile gcn with rocrand & hiprand, 

1.run script to modify library for rand
  ./modifyRandLib.sh
  this script does below
    /opt/rocm-4.0.0/include/hiprand/hiprand_hcc.h
    - #include <rocrand.h>
    + #include <rocrand/rocrand.h>

    /opt/rocm-4.0.0/include/hiprand/hiprand_kernel.h
    - #include <hiprand.h>
    + #include <hiprand/hiprand.h>

    /opt/rocm-4.0.0/include/hiprand/hiprand_kernel_hcc.h
    - #include <rocrand_kernel.h>
    + #include <rocrand/rocrand_kernel.h>

2.set environment variables with 
  $> source env.source
